Interface IMasteringProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MasteringProvider

    public interface IMasteringProvider
    Interface of the mastering provider.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.

      • getMasteringInfo

        com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.positionMastering.PositionMasteringInfo getMasteringInfo(String toolId)
        Returns the current complete state of the position mastering for all axes.
      • state of the position mastering [unmastered|mastered]
      • state of the encoder references [missing|existing]
      • state of the tool offsets if a valid tool identifier is provided [missing|existing]
Parameters:
toolId - tool identifier [UUID], may be null or "NO_TOOL" if no tool is used
Returns:
the current complete state of position mastering.
This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.

                                                                                          throws MasteringException
    Starts to check mastering for the given joint. Tool offset is not checked.

    masteringMethod - the used method
    jointIndex - zero based index of the axis/joint
    toolId - tool identifier [UUID], may be null or "NO_TOOL" if no tool is used
    Returns:
    the mastering check result containing current and new values for motor position, encoder reference and so on, tool offset data is null
    Throws:

    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
